high_descs: Turn around and approach the white table.
Pick up the green sponge on the front, right corner of the table.
Turn to your right and go to the stove.
Place the green sponge in the pan on the back, right burner of the stove.
Pick up the pan with the sponge inside it, from the stove.
Turn around and go back to the white table.
Place the pan with the sponge inside it on the right, front corner of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan containing a sponge on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and face a small white table.
Pick up the sponge to the right of the knife.
Walk to the stove on the right.
Put the sponge in the pan on the back burner.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Walk back over to the white table.
Put the pan down on the table to the right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: To put a sponge in a pan and put the pan down on the table.

high_descs: Turn around completely and face the table.
Pick up the sponge from the table.
Walk around the table turn left then right to face the stove.
Place the sponge in the frying pan on the stove.
Pick up the sponge and frying pan from the stove.
Turn around to the right and walk back around the table.
Place the frying pan and sponge on the table.
anns.task_desc: Move a frying pan and sponge to the table.
